{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"59a61206ecff4cfb59bceeaa022c87473d7d0ba6f2ed9b940607035e84227204","slug":"data-science","location":"/profile/qtclass/course/data_science.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"数据科学","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/profile/qtclass/course/data_science.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/profile/qtclass/course/data_science.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"data_science.md","url":"/data_science-940e378b3c18db04000135ae0c62de76.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"预测分析","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"ni8nSBeWrn"}],"identifier":"id","label":"预测分析","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"b0NMwZ0YQJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果我们已经有了小红书数据，怎么预测哪些线索有更高的概率转化成客户？比如说有一些帖子提出了去问大数据专业怎么去学习呀，怎么去找工作呀，要不要去选这个专业等等，那么对于量潮课堂来说的话，我们有咨询服务，有实训服务，也那么也也有一些课程的服务啊，他们有没有可能需要怎么从他们的一些话语包括评论啊，包括他们自己的评论啊，或者包括评论区的评论等等去，就假在假设有我们这些数据都有的情况之下，从他帖子或者评论的出发，就哪些是更有可能去获得的，哪些可能会比较困难。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"jzvypXGJrr"}],"key":"i28pTUALWw"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个是商业数据分析的一个常见需求，就是通过历史数据、各种内外部公开，内部数据和外部公开数据去找到，可能去提高效率的方法，通常情况下，我们更关心它能不能准确地去预测，我们的行为是不是有效，因此对于预测的准确性非常的关注。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"uLcQnlQlzA"}],"key":"hqA49XpLrd"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因果推断","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"P3q8NaCD9v"}],"identifier":"id","label":"因果推断","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"v6otWdVQdl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"挖掘这门课程的历史文档，找学习效果和学习活动的因果关系。怎么定义学习效果？怎么从自身出发寻找影响因素？怎么建立因果关系链画图？周会让大家先给出一些方向和定性结论。课程上，把当前课程的文档作为历史资料来分析。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"RQObdnD1fU"}],"key":"MLKk0m5hsh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因果推断的主要作用呢，是给决策层提供比较明确的解释，让决策层和团队知道自己做的事情为什么是对的，以及如何去扩大优势，就是看清楚情况，去简化决策难度。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"YU2TLXKC7A"}],"key":"WXKSioNvHp"}],"key":"zkepXHXeBM"}],"key":"sx6Az0vifx"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}